extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p This #[em app] helps you to keep track of all read books, as well as of ones on the wish list.

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p Your list has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Books:] !{data.book_count}
      li #[strong Authors:] !{data.author_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}